#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introdución"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; is a set of 3 tools with multiple functions. Firstly, it is a "
"convenient English to Japanese and Japanese to English dictionary; secondly, "
"it is a Kanji dictionary, with multiple ways to look up specific characters; "
"thirdly, it is a tool to help you learn Kanji."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; é un conxunto de tres ferramentas con varias funcións. En primeiro "
"lugar, é un dicionario de inglés-xaponés e xaponés-inglés cómodo; en segundo "
"lugar, é un dicionario de kanji, con varios modos de consulta de caracteres "
"específicos; en terceiro lugar, é unha ferramenta para axudar a aprender "
"kanji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each of these modes is discussed in its own chapter."
msgstr "Cada un destes modos trátase no seu propio capítulo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &kiten;"
msgstr "Velaquí unha captura de pantalla de &kiten;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; screenshot"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla de &kiten;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Dictionary"
msgstr "Uso do dicionario"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten;'s most basic mode is as a dictionary for looking up both English and "
"Japanese words. You can also add other dictionaries to &kiten;'s list."
msgstr ""
"O modo máis básico de &kiten; é como dicionario para consultar palabras "
"tanto en inglés como en kanji. Tamén se poden engadir outros dicionarios á "
"lista de &kiten;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kiten; uses Jim Breen's Edict and Kanjidic as the default dictionaries. "
#| "You can find more information at <ulink url=\"http://www.csse.monash.edu."
#| "au/~jwb/edict.html\">the Edict web site</ulink> and <ulink url=\"http://"
#| "www.csse.monash.edu.au/~jwb/kanjidic.html\">the Kanjidic web site</ulink>."
msgid ""
"&kiten; uses Jim Breen's Edict and Kanjidic as the default dictionaries. You "
"can find more information at <ulink url=\"https://www.edrdg.org/jmdict/edict."
"html\">the Edict web site</ulink> and <ulink url=\"https://www.edrdg.org/"
"wiki/index.php/KANJIDIC_Project\">the Kanjidic web site</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"O &kiten; emprega os Edict e Kanjidic de Jim Breen como dicionarios "
"predeterminados. Pódese atopar máis información nos sitios web de <ulink url="
"\"http://www.csse.monash.edu.au/~jwb/edict.html\">Edict</ulink> e <ulink url="
"\"http://www.csse.monash.edu.au/~jwb/kanjidic.html\">Kanjidic</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Looking Up Words"
msgstr "Consulta de palabras"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To look up words in either language, type them in to the text-edit (much "
#| "like &konqueror;'s location bar) and press either &Enter; or the "
#| "<guilabel>Search</guilabel> button on the toolbar (again, much like "
#| "&konqueror;). &kiten; will then look up the word."
msgid ""
"To look up words in either language, type them in to the text-edit (much "
"like &konqueror;'s location bar) and press either &Enter; or the "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton> button on the toolbar (again, much like "
"&konqueror;). &kiten; will then look up the word."
msgstr ""
"Para consultar palabras en calquera idioma, escríbeas no editor de texto "
"(similar á barra de localización de &konqueror;) e preme &Enter; ou o botón "
"<guilabel>Buscar</guilabel> da barra de ferramentas (de novo, similar á de "
"&konqueror;). &kiten; busca a palabra."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter Kanji, Kana and English and get back results from &kiten;. "
"These results of your search will appear in the large results view which "
"takes up the majority of the &kiten; window."
msgstr ""
"Pódese inserir kanji, kana e inglés e obter os resultados de &kiten;. Os "
"resultados da busca aparecen na vista de resultados grande que ocupa a maior "
"parte da xanela de &kiten;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "searching for an English translation"
msgstr "Busca dunha tradución ao inglés"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; search screenshot"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla da busca en &kiten;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filtering"
msgstr "Filtrado"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Often times you will want to filter rare words from your search. &kiten; "
"will do this for you if toggle <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Filter Out Rare</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Con frecuencia quérense filtrar as falabras raras. &kiten; faino se se "
"escolle <menuchoice><guimenu>Buscar</guimenu><guimenuitem>Filtrar o raro</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not all dictionary files support filtering rare entries - most dictionaries, "
"excluding the two provided by default in &kiten; do not."
msgstr ""
"Non todos os ficheiros de dicionario admiten filtrar as entradas raras - a "
"maioría dos dicionarios, salvo os dous que &kiten; fornece de maneira "
"predeterminada, non o fan."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot using filtering of rare words"
msgstr "Captura da pantalla usando o filtrado de palabras rara"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; filtering search"
msgstr "Busca con filtro de &kiten;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common/Uncommon words"
msgstr "Palabras frecuentes/infrecuentes"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another way to separate information is to filter common and uncommon words, "
"this is useful when you want to focus on the common words and/or have "
"interest on uncommon ones. The only difference between Filter Out Rare and "
"Common/Uncommon options is that here you also get the Rare/Uncommon results."
msgstr ""
"Outra maneira de separación a información é filtras as palabras frecuentes e "
"as infrecuentes; isto é útil cando se quere centrarse nas palabras "
"frecuentes e/ou se ten interese nas infrecuentes. A única diferenza entre "
"opcións Filtrar as raras e Frecuente/Infrecuente é que aquí tamén se poden "
"obter resultados Raras/Infrecuentes."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for match common/uncommon"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla para coincidir coas frecuentes/infrecuentes"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; match common/uncommon"
msgstr "Coincidir coas frecuentes/infrecuentes de &kiten;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Searches"
msgstr "Buscas avanzadas"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; supports more advanced searches than plain normal word searches."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; admiten buscas máis avanzadas que as buscas normais de palabras."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Beginning/Ending/Anywhere Searches"
msgstr "Buscas Comezando por/Rematando por/En calquera sitio"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Beside a search with <guilabel>Exact Match</guilabel> &kiten; has three "
#| "additional search modes"
msgid ""
"Beside a search with <guilabel>Exact Match</guilabel> &kiten; has three "
"additional search modes."
msgstr ""
"Ademais da busca con <guilabel>Equivalencia exacta</guilabel>, &kiten; "
"dispón de tres modos de busca adicionais"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To search for the beginning of a word, instead of pressing the "
#| "<guilabel>Search</guilabel> button on the toolbar or pressing "
#| "<keycap>Return</keycap> on the text-entry in the toolbar, choose using "
#| "the <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu><guisubmenu>Match Type </"
#| "guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Match Beginning</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
#| "Similarly, for ending or anywhere searches, choose "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Match Type</"
#| "guisubmenu></menuchoice> <guimenuitem>Match Anywhere</guimenuitem> or "
#| "<guimenuitem>Match Ending</guimenuitem> to search for your text anywhere "
#| "in or at the end of a word. These search modes work for searches of both "
#| "languages."
msgid ""
"To search for the beginning of a word, instead of pressing the "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton> button on the toolbar or pressing &Enter; on "
"the text-entry in the toolbar, choose using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Match Type </guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Match Beginning</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Similarly, for ending or anywhere searches, "
"choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Match Type</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> <guimenuitem>Match Anywhere</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Match Ending</guimenuitem> to search for your text anywhere in "
"or at the end of a word. These search modes work for searches of both "
"languages."
msgstr ""
"Para buscar polo inicio dunha palabra, no canto de premer o botón "
"<guilabel>Buscar</guilabel> da barra de tarefas ou premer <keycap>Intro</"
"keycap> no editor de texto da barra de tarefas, escolla "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Buscar</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tipo de equivalencia</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Coincidir co inicio</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. De "
"xeito similar, escolla <menuchoice><guimenu>Buscar</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tipo "
"de equivalencia</guisubmenu></menuchoice> <guimenuitem>Coincidir con "
"calquera</guimenuitem> ou <guimenuitem>Coincidir co final</guimenuitem> para "
"buscar texto en calquera parte dunha palabra ou ao final. Estes modos de "
"busca funcionan nas buscas nos dous idiomas."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for match ending search"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla para coincidir coa busca ao final"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; match ending search"
msgstr "Coincidir coa busca ao final de &kiten;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Word type searches"
msgstr "Busca de tipos de palabra"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; supports word type searches such as: verb, noun, adjective, "
#| "adverb, prefix, suffix, expression or any type. This way you can filter "
#| "your results more conveniently."
msgid ""
"&kiten; supports word type searches such as: verb, noun, adjective, adverb, "
"prefix, suffix, expression or any type. This way you can filter your results "
"more conveniently."
msgstr ""
"O &kappname; permite realizar buscas polo tipo de palabra, como verbo, "
"substantivo, adxectivo, adverbio, prefixo, sufixo, expresión ou calquera "
"tipo. Así pódense filtrar os resultados máis comodamente."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for match word type"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla para coincidir co tipo de palabra"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; match word type"
msgstr "Coincidir co tipo de palabra de &kiten;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching in Results"
msgstr "Buscar nos resultados"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; can also help you refine your searches by allowing you to search for "
"new text in the results generated by a previous search. To do this, just "
"choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu><guimenuitem>Search in Results</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to perform your search. Similarly to beginning/"
"ending/anywhere searches, this works for both languages too."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; tamén pode axudar a refinar as buscas permitindo buscar texto novo "
"nos resultados xerados por unha busca anterior. Para facelo, escolla "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Buscar</guimenu><guimenuitem>Buscar nos resultados</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. De maneira similar ás buscas polo principio/final/"
"calquera parte, isto funciona tamén nos dous idiomas."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for search in results"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla para buscar nos resultados"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; search in results"
msgstr "Busca nos resultados de &kiten;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Looking Up Kanji"
msgstr "Consulta de kanji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; has features that makes finding the one kanji you want easy from "
"over 14,000 in the default dictionary."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; ten funcionalidades que facilitan atopar o kanji que se quere de "
"entre os 14.000 que hai no dicionario predeterminado."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on any Kanji in the main result view will show details on that "
"particular Kanji. This can sometimes be the fastest way to look up a Kanji."
msgstr ""
"Ao premer calquera kanji da vista principal de resultados aparecen detalles "
"sobre ese kanji en concreto. Esta pode ser ás veces a forma máis rápida de "
"consultar un kanji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kanji searches are also filtered according to whether "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu><guimenuitem>Filter Out Rare</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> is checked."
msgstr ""
"As buscas de kanji tamén se filtran segundo marcase "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Buscar</guimenu><guimenuitem>Filtrar o raro</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Regular Searching"
msgstr "Buscas con expresións regulares"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can search with English and Japanese search strings the exact same way "
"you can with the normal dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Pódense buscar cadeas en inglés e en xaponés do mesmo xeito que se pode nun "
"dicionario normal."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Radical Searching"
msgstr "Buscar raíces"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use &kiten;'s radical search dialog to search for Kanji with a "
"combination of radicals and a certain stroke count. Choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu><guimenuitem>Radical Selector</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to open the radical search dialog."
msgstr ""
"Pódese usar o diálogo de busca de raíces de &kiten; para buscar kanji cunha "
"combinación de radicais que teñan un determinado número de trazos. Escolla "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Buscar</guimenu><guimenuitem>Selector de radicais</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> para abrir o diálogo de busca de radicais."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To choose the radicals you want to be in your Kanji, select one them from "
"the buttons at the bottom of the window. To display possible radicals to "
"select from this buttons with a certain number of strokes, choose this "
"number of strokes from the spinboxes just above the buttons. The radicals "
"you choose will appear in the listbox at the top."
msgstr ""
"Para escoller os radicais que quere que estean no kanji, escolla un nos "
"botóns que hai no fondo da xanela. Para que aparezan os radicais posíbeis de "
"entre os que escoller nestes botóns que teñan un determinado número de "
"trazos, escolla este número nos selectores que hai xusto por riba dos "
"botóns. Os radicais que escolla aparecerán na caixa de selección de arriba."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To choose how many strokes your Kanji should have, just enter the values "
"into the spin boxes below the results area."
msgstr ""
"Para escoller o número de trazos que desexe que teña o kanji, simplemente "
"insira os valores nos selectores que hai por baixo da área de resultados."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To perform the lookup, press the button that matches the kanji you wanted to "
"look up."
msgstr ""
"Para realizar a busca, prema o botón que coincida co kanji que quere "
"consultar."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for radical selector"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla do selector de radical"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; radical selector"
msgstr "Selector de radical de &kiten;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grade Search"
msgstr "Busca de graos"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get a list of all Kanji in a certain grade, enter that into the search "
"box as \"G:1\" (G: is the Kanjidic tag for grade)."
msgstr ""
"Para obter unha lista de todos os kanji dun determinado grao, insíreo na "
"caixa de buscas como «G:1» (G: é a etiqueta en kanji para grao)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for kanji grade search"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla da busca nos graos de kanji"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; kanji grade search"
msgstr "Busca nos graos de kanji de &kiten;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stroke Search"
msgstr "Buscas por trazos"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:307
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To get a list of all Kanji with a certain number of strokes, enter that "
#| "number in the text-entry in the toolbar as \"S:2\"."
msgid ""
"To get a list of all Kanji with a certain number of strokes, enter that "
"number the search box as \"S:2\"."
msgstr ""
"Para obter unha lista de todos os kanji que teñen un determinado número de "
"trazos, introduce ese número no editor de texto da barra de tarefas como "
"«S:2»."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for kanji strokes search"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla da busca dos trazos dos kanji"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; kanji strokes search"
msgstr "Busca dos trazos dos kanji de &kiten;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kanji List"
msgstr "Lista de kanji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This part of the Kanji Browser lets you visualize a list of kanji filtered "
"by grade and number of strokes. By Clicking on a kanji you can get detailed "
"information about it. Kanji Browser separates the list in Jouyou, Jinmeiyou "
"and non-Jouyou kanji. All this kanji is available thanks to the KANJIDIC "
"dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Esta parte do navegador de kanji permite ver unha lista de kanji filtrados "
"polo grao e o número de trazos. Ao premer un kanji obtense información "
"detallada sobre el. O navegador de kanji separa a lista en kanji Jouyou, "
"Jinmeiyou e non Jouyou. Todos estes kanji están dispoñíbeis grazas ao "
"dicionario KANJIDIC."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for kanji list"
msgstr "Captura de pantalla da lista de kanji"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; kanji list"
msgstr "Lista de kanji de &kiten;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kanji Information"
msgstr "Información sobre o kanji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This part shows you detailed information about a kanji such as: kanji stroke "
"order, number of strokes, readings and meanings."
msgstr ""
"Esta parte mostra información detallada sobre os kanji, como orde dos "
